stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> TelemetryIngest
    TelemetryIngest --> Planner

    Planner --> Risk

    Risk --> HighRiskEscalation: risk_score > threshold
    Risk --> CarrierLookup: risk_score <= threshold

    CarrierLookup --> RouteOptimizer: carriers_found
    CarrierLookup --> CarrierLookup: retry (transient lookup error, retries < max)
    CarrierLookup --> NoViableRouteEscalation: no carriers after max retries

    RouteOptimizer --> Validator: candidate_route_proposed
    RouteOptimizer --> NoViableRouteEscalation: no feasible route

    Validator --> Execution: route_valid
    Validator --> RouteOptimizer: route_invalid (retry < max)
    Validator --> NoViableRouteEscalation: route_invalid (retry == max)

    Execution --> Audit: execution_confirmed
    Execution --> Execution: retry (transient exec error, retries < max)
    Execution --> ExecutionFailedEscalation: execution failed after max retries

    Audit --> [*]: SUCCESS
    HighRiskEscalation --> [*]: ESCALATED
    NoViableRouteEscalation --> [*]: ESCALATED
    ExecutionFailedEscalation --> [*]: FAILED
